headline: KLA Corporation (KLAC) Stock Is Up, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of semiconductor manufacturing equipment maker KLA Corporation (NASDAQ:KLAC) jumped 2.7% in the afternoon session after analyst sentiment turned more positive, highlighted by a significant price target increase from Citigroup.
